## Top Recommendation: **Conlun Cat Litter Mat (B0CP5PBGFW) - £8.99**

### Why This Is My #1 Pick for HappyPawsCo:

**1. Perfect Blog Alignment**
- **Size:** 58x42cm gives cats the "2-3 steps" your blog emphasizes for effective litter capture
- **Double-layer honeycomb:** Matches your highlighted section perfectly - litter falls through and gets trapped below
- **Waterproof bottom:** Direct match to your "waterproof backing is essential" guidance

**2. Proven Performance**
- 2,939 reviews with 4.1⭐ rating shows sustained customer satisfaction
- 400+ bought in the past month = currently trending
- Multiple size options (58x42, 60x46, 76x61) let you test or offer choice

**3. Business Benefits**
- **Best delivery:** Prime tomorrow (11 Jan) = meets your 2-5 working day requirement easily
- **Mid-range pricing:** £8.99 positions well between budget Adiwo (£6.99) and premium options
- **Save 5% on 4 items** - you can promote this for customers buying multiple pet products
- **Strong profit margin potential:** Can be marked up to £15.99-£18.99 on HappyPawsCo while still being competitive

**4. Customer Objection Handling**
- **1-2 star feedback** shows addressable concerns:
  - Edge curling → You can add care instructions in product copy
  - Initial cat reluctance → Your blog already covers the adjustment period
  - Very active cats → Position as "works best with covered or high-sided trays" (which you also sell)

**5. Content Marketing Fit**
- The yellow tray imagery in product photos creates visual interest and demonstrates use-case
- Easy to create comparison content: "Why double-layer beats single-layer"
- Can bundle with your top-entry or high-sided litter trays as a "Complete Litter Tracking Solution"

### How to Use in AutoDS:
1. **ASIN:** B0CP5PBGFW
2. **Import URL:** https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B0CP5PBGFW
3. **Set Pricing:** £15.99-£18.99 (80-112% markup)
4. **Shipping:** Map to "Standard UK Delivery" - AutoDS will handle Amazon Prime fulfilment
5. **Product Title:** Keep "Honeycomb Double Layer" and "Waterproof" prominent
6. **Link to Blog:** Add your "Stop Cat Litter Tracking" article in the product description

**Alternative for premium customers:** If they want the absolute best, upsell the **Gorilla Grip (B07GYZPM94)** at £37.99-£42.99 as your "Premium Choice" - highest rating (4.4⭐) and softer material, but note the slower delivery in your copy.